Build: Customer List Page (app/(admin)/customers/page.js)

Context

Refer to CLAUDE.md for full project context, stack, folder structure, database schema, and Supabase client conventions before writing any code. This page lives inside the admin layout shell — do not rebuild the sidebar or header.


What to build

A page at app/(admin)/customers/page.js showing a searchable, filterable table of all customers on the platform. No create functionality here — customers are created from the NFC Items page. This page is read-focused with lightweight management actions.

This is a Client Component ('use client').


Performance requirements


Fetch all customer data in a single query — join user_roles, profiles, and a count of nfc_items per customer. No per-row follow-up requests.
Debounce search input at 300ms using useRef timer — no library.
Use useMemo for all filtering and sorting — never recompute on every render.
Client-side pagination — fetch all, slice locally. 10 rows per page.
Skeleton loading state for the table on initial load — never a full-page spinner.



