Account status logic

Derive the status badge from the combination of last_sign_in_at and email_confirmed_at on the auth user:


email_confirmed_at is null → Invited (amber badge) — invite sent but not accepted yet
email_confirmed_at exists + last_sign_in_at is null → Active (green badge) — accepted invite but never logged in yet
email_confirmed_at exists + last_sign_in_at exists → Active (green badge)


Render as a shadcn/ui Badge with appropriate color variant.

