Relative time helper

Write a small pure function formatRelativeTime(dateString) in lib/utils.js:

"just now"       → less than 1 minute ago
"X minutes ago"  → 1–59 minutes
"X hours ago"    → 1–23 hours
"X days ago"     → 1–6 days
"X weeks ago"    → 1–3 weeks
"X months ago"   → 1–11 months
"X years ago"    → 12+ months
null/undefined   → "Never"

Use Date.now() and Date.parse() only — no library.


